<h3>What's a humans.md file?</h3>
<p>Find everything you need to know about the PHIX 2015 theme. There are steps on how to create sprites, what references were used to create the theme, how to build new LESS files and more.</p>
<p>The human.md file lives in <code>ghix-web/src/main/webapp/resources/humans.md</code>.</p>

<h4>Learn how to:</h4>
<ul>
	<li>Grunt SVG, PNG, images into Sprites</li>
	<li>How to put the sprite into your HTML</li>
</ul>

<h4>Grunt.js Intro</h4>
<p>Start with this to get <a href="http://24ways.org/2013/grunt-is-not-weird-and-hard/">Grunt</a> running.</p>

